{"tid":175901,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家入黎駁下我","createTime":"2017-03-27T21:13:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T11:21:51.000Z","uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ee82c8bb969ca8ea6d6951e8e64c97ef93a12024","tid":175901,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T21:13:08.000Z","msg":"我諗到個新講法推廣 ATV，請各位巴打駁下傾下，等個講法完善啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實支唔支持 ATV 都係講大家想要咩，同埋信唔信 TVB<br />\n<br />\n大家既終極目標(正路黎講)都係為睇好節目，咁可能有人覺得 TVB 就系好，有人覺得 外購劇 就系好，有人覺得 有創意 就系好。<br />\n<br />\n所以例如一個人覺得 TVB 就系好，而佢又信 中共 會畀到 TVB 你，所以就會支持 TVB 管 茶餐廳部電視機<br />\n<br />\n咁如果一個人覺得 有創意 系好，而又唔信 TVB 畀到你，支持 長開播住TVB 系完全唔合理既選擇，所以應該考慮轉台睇 ATV香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef664d1bc6a8fa4a981e1a7331d033803950b64c","tid":175901,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T21:29:09.000Z","msg":"大家係指邊個？"},{"pid":"eb7416993c67add89673bc64d198f885dde27b42","tid":175901,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:22:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家係指邊個？</blockquote><br />\nPls ask this 巴打<br />\n<br />\n大家入嚟駁下我<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/174861/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/174861/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d9d55285414aea59fd6912352d09ba77f65ac5d3","tid":175901,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T02:26:27.000Z","msg":"Atv?"},{"pid":"4868475c38dcad4ba45bf9720233e833ce3663df","tid":175901,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T09:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/di9nt5ly\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdi9nt5ly&h=788f1b8a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"159422bfd51b0b32ecf833867fe7643d28f0976c","tid":175901,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply